VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bNativeModules\.DevSettings\b|\bDevSettings\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:__DEV__|if.*__DEV__|kDebugMode|// development only
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Metro bundler DevSettings module access that may not be guarded by a debug-only check.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Metro Bundler DevSettings Accessed Outside Debug Guard.
